  "detailed_description": "<strong>Delve into an intricate story about a grieving father, who finds himself involved in paranormal events related to a secretive cult and a mysterious girl.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/f1bada800402008136694ac6263999fb.poster.avif?t=1757543195\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/f1bada800402008136694ac6263999fb.webm?t=1757543195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/f1bada800402008136694ac6263999fb.mp4?t=1757543195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Repent</h2>Explore the story of Robert Watford, a retired cop with a heavy alcohol addiction and troubled past, as he starts his new job as a night shift guard of the Colony Tower. Rob will find himself in the middle of paranormal events involving a strange girl and a mysterious cult, leaving him no choice but to take matters into his own hands to try to understand what's happening and why. Rob will face various instances in which his decisions directly affect the outcome of the story and the people involved.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/4460a55e89ed23f19e9ec82defe3b1ed.poster.avif?t=1757543195\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/4460a55e89ed23f19e9ec82defe3b1ed.webm?t=1757543195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/4460a55e89ed23f19e9ec82defe3b1ed.mp4?t=1757543195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>Repent is primarily a first-person narrative walking simulator that focuses on exploration. The player will be able to complete tasks and interact with the tenants of the Colony Tower through conversations or secondary events, to learn more about the location, its people and the many mysteries that lie within the building. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/268f5906a661d67952661dcad2af919e.poster.avif?t=1757543195\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/268f5906a661d67952661dcad2af919e.webm?t=1757543195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/268f5906a661d67952661dcad2af919e.mp4?t=1757543195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Conversation system with various dialog options.<br></li><li> Deep story with multiple endings.<br></li><li> Immersion focused horror.<br></li><li> Randomly generated secondary events, making each playthrough unique.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Delve into an intricate story about a grieving father, who finds himself involved in paranormal events related to a secretive cult and a mysterious girl.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/f1bada800402008136694ac6263999fb.poster.avif?t=1757543195\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/f1bada800402008136694ac6263999fb.webm?t=1757543195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/f1bada800402008136694ac6263999fb.mp4?t=1757543195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Repent</h2>Explore the story of Robert Watford, a retired cop with a heavy alcohol addiction and troubled past, as he starts his new job as a night shift guard of the Colony Tower. Rob will find himself in the middle of paranormal events involving a strange girl and a mysterious cult, leaving him no choice but to take matters into his own hands to try to understand what's happening and why. Rob will face various instances in which his decisions directly affect the outcome of the story and the people involved.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/4460a55e89ed23f19e9ec82defe3b1ed.poster.avif?t=1757543195\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/4460a55e89ed23f19e9ec82defe3b1ed.webm?t=1757543195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/4460a55e89ed23f19e9ec82defe3b1ed.mp4?t=1757543195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\